room_title: Escape room "Head of the Class" by Escape The Hood in Hood River
room_description:
You and your classmates are the top of your class.

The future of our country depends on the development of next generation think tanks... But can you pass this one last test to gain approval for a vital mission?

Your skills will be tested... 

Can you and your team solve the puzzles and the mysteries within one hour?

Grab your friends, family, or co-workers and join the others that have tested their mental might to see if you can pass the final exam.
